# {{ .projectName }}

HashiCorp Vault secrets manager in development mode.

## Quick Start

    cp .env.example .env
    docker compose up -d

## Access

* Vault UI: http://localhost:{{ .vaultPort }}/ui
* Vault API: http://localhost:{{ .vaultPort }}

Sign in with the root token set in VAULT_DEV_ROOT_TOKEN_ID.

## CLI Usage

    export VAULT_ADDR=http://localhost:{{ .vaultPort }}
    export VAULT_TOKEN=dev-root-token
    vault kv put secret/myapp password=changeme
    vault kv get secret/myapp
